author: Ashley Weatherford
title: Louis Vuitton Ad, or True Detective Trailer?
text: For Louis Vuitton's latest cruise collection campaign, the French luxury giant takes us on a fantasy journey through the desert starring Michelle Williams and newly minted Louis Vuitton face Alicia Vikander . The duo travel to the scene of the brand's Palm Springs fashion show while employing True Detective– like dialog along the way. There are pensive stares, dramatic overtures, and even a dalliance with a snake. Click the video above to watch the women explore the airy desert wasteland with Louis Vuitton's newest handbags in tow.
